<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/12395050-neal-mcgrath"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1548337003i/12395050._UY100_CR1,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
