<div id="review_235213815" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/235213815" />
    <a title="Bro_Pair Ø£Ø¹Ø±Ù" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6956621-bro-pair"><img alt="Bro_Pair Ø£Ø¹Ø±Ù" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1321239908p2/6956621.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/235213815?book_show_action=true">Nov 13, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bro_Pair Ø£Ø¹Ø±Ù" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bro_Pair Ø£Ø¹Ø±Ù" href="/user/show/6956621-bro-pair">Bro_Pair Ø£Ø¹Ø±Ù</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6956621-bro-pair?shelf=carribean-queens">carribean-queens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6956621-bro-pair?shelf=the-fourth">the-fourth</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer235213815" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12289447580212260765">This is it, the bildungsroman to end all bildungsromans. Celine wields youth like a cudgel. What came before is dead and putrescent. It whistles and hums and steams for dozens of pages at a time before a periodic explosion of nightmarish dimensions. Gruesome suicides, mechanized robotic attacks, mad braying priests, violent domestic conflagrations. Celine uses the typewriter as a weapon - literally, in one passage. Read it. Read it now.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

