        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1431200574" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13004911142116136146">Unfinished, to be honest, but I didn&apos;t want to kindly reminders from goodreads that I started it ten billion years ago.<br/>Death by ellipses. Stylistically not my thing, and it&apos;s never particularly interesting to hear someone complain about their work. Tolstoy got it wrong; it&apos;s the unhappy that are all the same. Our depressions/anxieties/pessimistic outlook don&apos;t make us any more of an artiste, I am afraid -- otherwise I&apos;d be the next Shakespeare.</span>
  <span id="freeText13004911142116136146" style="display:none">Unfinished, to be honest, but I didn't want to kindly reminders from goodreads that I started it ten billion years ago.<br />Death by ellipses. Stylistically not my thing, and it's never particularly interesting to hear someone complain about their work. Tolstoy got it wrong; it's the unhappy that are all the same. Our depressions/anxieties/pessimistic outlook don't make us any more of an artiste, I am afraid -- otherwise I'd be the next Shakespeare.</span>
